room_title: Escape room "The Pirates Wreck Room" by UnlockaLock Escape Room in Chicago
review: It was really fun. It was very challenging but not impossible. We did not escape but still had a blast. We did the Pirate room and are planning on going back to do the throne room. Great night out for your group.

room_title: Escape room "The Pirates Wreck Room" by UnlockaLock Escape Room in Chicago
review: The Pirate room was really tough! Definitely gave my brain some exercise...

room_title: Escape room "The Pirates Wreck Room" by UnlockaLock Escape Room in Chicago
review: This was a great place! We did the Pirate Room and really enjoyed it. The people running the room owned the place and cleared really cared about us having a great time. The room was very challenging and clever! We saw things we hadn't seen anywhere else. Highly recommend.
